      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Goal — proposal\n\n**Purpose**: Represents a desired outcome. Strategic or local.\n\n**Canonical fields**:\n- `label` (string)\n- `description` (markdown)\n- `priority` (low | medium | high | critical)\n- `status` (open | active | achieved | abandoned)\n- `scope` (strategic | local)\n\n**Rules**:\n- Goals do not carry tasks; tasks carry goals via edges.\n- A goal may have child goals (decomposition).\n- Completion state lives on the goal, not inferred from tasks.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
