      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Decision — proposal\n\n**Purpose**: Records a resolved choice, its rationale, and status.\n\n**Canonical fields**:\n- `label` (string)\n- `body` (markdown — rationale)\n- `status` (proposed | accepted | superseded | reversed)\n- `date` (ISO 8601)\n- `supersedes` (node ID, optional)\n\n**Rules**:\n- Decisions are append-only in intent. Use `supersedes` to chain.\n- A Decision can resolve an Open Question (edge: `resolves`).\n- A Decision can authorize relaxing a Constraint (edge: `overrides`).\n- Codex should treat accepted decisions as authoritative.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
