      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Open Question — proposal\n\n**Purpose**: Captures an unresolved question that blocks or informs decisions.\n\n**Canonical fields**:\n- `label` (string)\n- `body` (markdown)\n- `status` (open | investigating | resolved | deferred)\n- `owner` (string, optional)\n- `resolution` (markdown, optional — filled on close)\n\n**Rules**:\n- Resolution converts status to `resolved`, does not delete the node.\n- Resolution should produce a Decision or Task (edge: `resolved-by`).\n- Unresolved open questions should be surfaced prominently in prompts.\n- Distinct from Risk: a question is epistemic, a risk is probabilistic.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
