      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Task — proposal\n\n**Purpose**: A discrete, implementable unit of work.\n\n**Canonical fields**:\n- `label` (string)\n- `body` (markdown — description + context)\n- `status` (todo | in-progress | done | blocked | cancelled)\n- `priority` (low | medium | high | critical)\n- `owner` (string, optional)\n- `estimate` (string, optional — e.g. \"2h\", \"S/M/L\")\n\n**Rules**:\n- Tasks should be scoped to one implementation unit.\n- A task may have one or more Acceptance Criteria nodes.\n- Tasks connect to Goals via `implements` edges.\n- Static by default. No live behavior unless explicitly promoted.\n- Maps directly to an execution prompt when status is `todo`.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
