          "type": "any"
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Acceptance Criteria — proposal\n\n**Purpose**: Defines when a Task or Goal is considered complete.\n\n**Canonical fields**:\n- `label` (string)\n- `items` (array of strings — checklist format)\n- `body` (markdown — optional prose supplement)\n- `format` (checklist | prose | test-spec)\n- `verified` (boolean, default false)\n\n**Rules**:\n- Attach to Tasks via `verifies` edges; may also attach to Goals.\n- Checklist format is preferred — it is unambiguous for Codex.\n- Prose format is allowed but should be used only when criteria are non-enumerable.\n- `verified: true` does not automatically mark the Task as done — it is a signal, not a trigger.\n- May eventually drive auto-review; `test-spec` format reserved for that path.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
