        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Risk / Edge Case — proposal\n\n**Purpose**: Names a probabilistic or boundary condition that could affect outcomes.\n\n**Canonical fields**:\n- `label` (string)\n- `body` (markdown)\n- `kind` (risk | edge-case) — keep combined for now, split later if needed\n- `severity` (low | medium | high | critical)\n- `likelihood` (low | medium | high)\n- `mitigation` (markdown, optional)\n- `status` (open | mitigated | accepted | escalated)\n\n**Rules**:\n- Escalation path: `status: escalated` converts to a Task or Decision (edge: `escalates-to`).\n- Edge cases connect to Acceptance Criteria via `covered-by` edges.\n- Distinct from Open Question: a risk is known, probabilistic. A question is unknown.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
