      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Arch: Dependency resolution\n\n**Decision**: Dependency is both node and edge, with distinct use-cases.\n\nEdge (`depends-on`) = ordering only.\nNode = first-class entity with status, kind, and source.\n\nThis resolves the node-vs-edge tension. The Dependency node proposal above encodes the full rule.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
