      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Arch: Execution linkage\n\nA Task with `status: todo` + its connected Acceptance Criteria + its connected Constraints + its parent Goal = the natural prompt bundle for Codex.\n\nNo separate 'execution context' node type is needed yet. The traversal from a Task node provides the context. If prompt shaping becomes complex, promote to a node type later.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
